headline: How Will the Stock Market Perform in 2025? The Experts Can't Agree. Here's What You Should Do.
summary: Here's a look at a range of expert predictions, along with some thoughts on what you might do to position yourself well for 2025 and beyond.  Goldman Sachs research has forecast that the S&P 500 will gain 10% in 2025.  Its experts expect that tariffs from the incoming administration along with expected tax cuts might "roughly offset one another."
